         <div type="translation">
            <ab>" Ç«· The holy church of God at Hermoupolis through me, Kollouthos, administrator of the share of Hermoupolis, to Kollouthos, hay-dealer. You have paid for the rent of the crops of the twelfth indiction seven and a half keratia of gold, total 7 1/2 ker. Written on Thoth 6 of the 12th indiction. Ç«·I, Kollouthos, administrator, agree.Ç«·"</ab>
         </div>
